<sect1 id="dir_2066a05c7cbde581e22905260647742b_1autotoc_md217">
<title>helios::engine::runtime::spawn::behavior::initializers</title><para>Concrete SpawnInitializer implementations.</para>
</sect1>
<sect1 id="dir_2066a05c7cbde581e22905260647742b_1autotoc_md218">
<title>Overview</title><para>This module provides ready-to-use SpawnInitializer implementations for configuring spawned entities.</para>
</sect1>
<sect1 id="dir_2066a05c7cbde581e22905260647742b_1autotoc_md219">
<title>Key Classes</title><para><table rows="3" cols="2"><row>
<entry thead="yes"><para>Class  </para>
</entry><entry thead="yes"><para>Purpose  </para>
</entry></row>
<row>
<entry thead="no"><para><computeroutput>EmitterInitializer</computeroutput>  </para>
</entry><entry thead="no"><para>Configures entity direction/velocity based on emitter state  </para>
</entry></row>
<row>
<entry thead="no"><para><computeroutput>RandomDirectionInitializer</computeroutput>  </para>
</entry><entry thead="no"><para>Applies a random 2D direction to spawned entities  </para>
</entry></row>
</table>
</para>
</sect1>
<sect1 id="dir_2066a05c7cbde581e22905260647742b_1autotoc_md220">
